test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [-3, -3] == [-3]
  Left contains one more item: -3
  Full diff:
  - [-3]
  + [-3, -3]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0] == [0]
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0]
  + [0, 0]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [90] == []
  Left contains one more item: 90
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [90]
